@startuml Deployment Diagram
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
top to bottom direction

node "Client Machine" as Client {
    artifact "Web Browser" as Browser
    database "IndexedDB" as LocalDB
}

node "Server Machine" as Server {
    artifact "Node.js Server" as NodeServer
    artifact "Socket.IO" as SocketIO
}

Browser --> NodeServer : HTTP/WebSocket\n(port 3001)
Browser --> LocalDB : Local Storage

note right of Browser
    Runs React app
    Handles UI, steganography,
    encryption, local storage
end note

note right of NodeServer
    Express server
    Handles real-time messaging
    Room management
end note

note right of LocalDB
    Client-side storage
    for message history
    No server persistence
end note

note right of SocketIO
    Enables real-time
    bidirectional communication
end note
@enduml
